metadata.name: Nakaturds #1
metadata.description: Aren't you sick of this shit? Well if you're not, one day in a metaverse far far away. A rare honorary Nakamigo (whose name will be un-mentioned but you probably know) was walking along his punk and witnessed something so explosive he shit through his pants. Fortunately for you now we can collect these magic pixel turds. Word has it you should nurture your turd and it will nurture you back.
